{"tid":1255194,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家好又係我林鄭月娥","createTime":"2019-06-24T11:48:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T11:48:10.000Z","uid":261349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"845c2bdeeab9cc953ce05c3f2d006898db93e6e7","tid":1255194,"uid":261349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T11:48:10.000Z","msg":"又係我林鄭，見到班中間派同反對派割哂蓆，班反對派自己又內訌，真係心都涼哂。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽講有人話我死期就到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />未出力咋死蠢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n知你班契弟唔識食住上，一句暫緩再加一句道歉就搞掂左。咩話？你地試過兩個禮拜既抗爭咁多呀？講出來都丟架啦廢柴。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「階段性勝利」喎，叫呀盧署長同班伙計抖下先，打都唔使打，班友就咩做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />到時民意逆轉仲唔扑濕你地班契弟？<br />\n咩輿論戰話？傳來傳去咪又自己果班，有咩用呀，拎來打飛機呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？我就唔同，叫呀李導演拍條假片，咁又呃到班家長。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n吓，建制大決裂？傻豬，你地決裂我地都未決裂呀！呢頭叫呀放小小風出來，個頭叫呀琼做下戲話要求撤回。成班友就以為有機，鬆懈到一個點，咪比我玩到tum tum轉囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家我控制住主流媒體，班傻閪咪繼續衝囉，唔使幾日民意又番哂來lu，諗起都爽。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有呀，聽講班有和理非又狗衝出來同人割蓆喎。之前仲聽講咩「兄弟爬山」，搞到我都有d顧忌添<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，就咁睇今日人數，當堂嚇左跳，仲諗住係我地請既果80慢人添！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 岩呀岩呀，你地慢慢玩內訌啦，咁睇來626瞓足成日都唔會比人搞到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。喂唔講啦，去瞓覺先！"}]}